## Anvil Setup

- **Anvil User Guide**: [link](https://www.rcac.purdue.edu/knowledge/anvil)

### Logging In
To log in, follow the instructions here: [https://www.rcac.purdue.edu/knowledge/anvil/access/login](https://www.rcac.purdue.edu/knowledge/anvil/access/login)

Start by generating an [SSH key](https://www.rcac.purdue.edu/knowledge/anvil/access/login/sshkeys) by following the steps provided in the link.

### Setup of Anvil Environment
Modify bashrc - Rachel will provide a model for what this should look like.

